Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:40.94,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}一路逞強至今
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:45.24,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}更顯腳步經歷銘心刻骨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:47.78,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8}輕率的玩笑也能傷人
